Example:

String s1 = "hello";
String s2 = "hello";

if(s1.equals(s2)){
    System.out.println("Equal");
}
8️⃣ Reverse a String

Basic interview question.

String s = "hello";

for(int i = s.length()-1; i >= 0; i--){
    System.out.print(s.charAt(i));
}

Output

olleh
9️⃣ Check Palindrome
String s = "madam";

int start = 0;
int end = s.length()-1;

boolean isPalindrome = true;

while(start < end){
    
    if(s.charAt(start) != s.charAt(end)){
        isPalindrome = false;
        break;
    }
    
    start++;
    end--;
}

System.out.println(isPalindrome);
🔟 Count Character Frequency (VERY COMMON)
String s = "banana";

int[] freq = new int[26];

for(int i = 0; i < s.length(); i++){
    
    char ch = s.charAt(i);
    
    freq[ch - 'a']++;
}

for(int i = 0; i < 26; i++){
    
    if(freq[i] > 0){
        System.out.println((char)(i+'a') + " -> " + freq[i]);
    }
}

Output

b -> 1
a -> 3
n -> 2
