4️⃣ Check Anagram

Two strings are anagram if they contain same characters with same frequency.

Example

listen
silent
Code
String s1 = "listen";
String s2 = "silent";

int[] freq = new int[26];

for(int i = 0; i < s1.length(); i++){
    freq[s1.charAt(i) - 'a']++;
}

for(int i = 0; i < s2.length(); i++){
    freq[s2.charAt(i) - 'a']--;
}

boolean isAnagram = true;

for(int i = 0; i < 26; i++){
    if(freq[i] != 0){
        isAnagram = false;
        break;
    }
}

System.out.println(isAnagram);
Concept

Use frequency array

Time complexity

O(n)
